With the new version ('Cantera155.msi') everything is working fine.
I no =
longer get negative mole fraction : ) Thanks, Dave!
When installing the new=
 version I had to create the user variable
'PYTHON_CMD' as described in the=
 installation manual. Adding the 
python directory to 'PATH' didn't work.
F=
urther I had to copy the file 'msvcp71.dll' (which you will find
in the new=
 Cantera directory, after having run 'Cantera155.msi') into
the directory C=
:\Program Files\Matlab6p5\bin\win32.

Bj=F6rn
